flowchart LR
    A([Dev Complete]) --> B[Peer Code Review]
    B --> C{Tests Pass?}
    C --> |Fail| A
    C --> |Pass| D[QA Validation]
    D --> E{QA Sign-off?}
    E --> |No| A
    E --> |Yes| F[Security Scan]
    F --> G{Clear?}
    G --> |No| H[Fix Vulnerabilities]
    H --> F
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION
    G --> |Yes| K[Compliance Review]
    K --> L{Compliant?}
    L --> |No| M[Address Compliance Issues]
    M --> K
    L --> |Yes| I[VP Engineering Approval]
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    I --> J([Production Release])